Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让弥勒他们变成那个样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定不是海神\N而是眼前的这个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:20:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海猫姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海草
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟海神是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来海猫姑娘跟海神\N都只是被操纵的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
