Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:21:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把铁碎牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把铁碎牙给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把铁碎牙\N已经在我的手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来她的目的是铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷  您怎么在这
