Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:58.75,ED,,0,0,0,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:14.80,ED,,0,0,0,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:20.87,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:24.40,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the dreaming
